data.description: ASSUMABLE FHA LOAN at 5.3% for qualified buyers!! Lender says if you are prequalified with your bank, you can close in 30-45 days. This move in ready home has a renovated interior, with new vinyl plank flooring on main level and upper level including bedrooms, a huge sunroom ready for your own choice of floor covering, an in-law suite on the terrace level with a kitchenette, huge bedroom and bath, new interior paint, renovated main kitchen with new appliances, counters, cabinets, and lighting. Beautiful gas starter fireplace in the family room, beautiful hardwood tongue in groove vaulted ceiling in family room. Driveway with extra parking as well as a 2 car garage. Large lot with creek, award winning schools and only 4 miles to I-75.
